            <section xml:id="classmain__menu_1ac653f7645e7dab1807f141ba2395dc5c">
                <title>void main_menu::show_menu ()</title> <emphasis>Show menu.</emphasis>
                
<para>This method shows the menu.
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
 <formalpara><title>Example: </title></formalpara>
</para>

<para><link linkend="classmain__menu_1ac653f7645e7dab1807f141ba2395dc5c">show_menu()</link> 
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
-&gt; You can now see the menu </para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="classmain__menu_1a9314da13b6b8a7cd40dee3d45f029835">
                <title>bool main_menu::button_pressed (picture &amp;object, sf::View &amp;view)</title> <emphasis>Ceck if a button is pressed.</emphasis>
                
<para>This method return a boolean if a menu button is pressed with the mouse or not.
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Parameters: </title></formalpara>
</para>

<para>object : picture&amp; 
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
-&gt; refference to picture class object &quot;object&quot;.
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
 view : sf::View&amp; 
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
-&gt; view where the mouse click is checked on.
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Return: </title></formalpara>
</para>

<para>button pressed : bool -&gt; button pressed with mouse</para>

<para><formalpara><title>Example: </title></formalpara>
</para>

<para>button_pressed(play_game, menu_view)
<literallayout>
</literallayout>
-&gt; true </para>

            </section>
            <section xml:id="classmain__menu_1a924f8d3f2d87b382a8590055cda2f549">
